This paper deals with object detection using deep CNN-based models, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of transfer learning and knowledge transfer, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also incorporates semantic relatedness, which is a topic in natural language processing (cs.CL), and visual similarity, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.MM.
